grassseedinc

Class GrassSeedInc

  • java.lang.Object
    • grassseedinc.GrassSeedInc

  • public class GrassSeedInc
extends java.lang.Object
    A program developed to solve the Grass Seed Inc problem from summer project competition issued to students between first and second year at Portsmouth university. See Readme for full details. This class takes 3 kinds of inputs, the cost to seed one square meter of lawn, the number of lawns and the width and length of each lawn, to calculates the cost and outputs it to the console.
